Title: General's Gambit: The Suicide Mission
Descriptions: Survivor, I have grave news. We've caught wind of a high-ranking Serpents meeting taking place at the North West Airfield. Several Colonels are gathering there, and the topic of discussion is a substance that goes by the name 'Alien Ore' and precious gems of unknown origin. These are no ordinary treasures, and they're worth a fortune. We need you to infiltrate that meeting, steal those Alien Ore ingots and gems, and bring them to Arvandus. He believes they hold the key to unraveling the mysteries of this world. However, I must be frank with you: this mission is next to impossible. Your chances of survival are slim, and you'll be up against some of the deadliest foes we've encountered. If you accept, you do so knowing the odds are stacked against you. The decision is yours.
